      "content": "budgeting doesnt fix the fact that im the problem. i look at the numbers and it literally makes more sense if im not here. like, the life insurance or even just the extra money they'd have without me paying for everything... it's just math. they'd breathe easier if they didnt have to worry about me failing them every day.",
